<bibRefCitation author="Perkins, P. D." box="[1267,1424,223,249]" pageId="7" pageNumber="432" pagination="3 - 554" refId="ref5273" refString="Perkins, P. D. (1980) Aquatic beetles of the family Hydraenidae in the Western Hemisphere: classification, biogeography and inferred phylogeny (Insecta: Coleoptera). Quaestiones entomologicae, 16, 3 - 554." type="journal article" year="1980">Perkins 1980</bibRefCitation>
). Small pool in a large expanse of sand dunes (
<bibRefCitation author="Valladares, L. F. &amp; Short, A. E. Z." box="[656,939,259,285]" pageId="7" pageNumber="432" pagination="63 - 68" refId="ref5932" refString="Valladares, L. F. &amp; Short, A. E. Z. (2011) Revision of the Ochthebiinae of Venezuela (Coleoptera: Hydraenidae). Zootaxa, 3021 (1), 63 - 68. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3021.1.4" type="journal article" year="2011">Valladares &amp; Short 2011</bibRefCitation>
